errorcode
Element


errorcode
&errorcode.purpose;


&errorcode.synopsis.gen;
Description



An error code. Error codes are often numeric, but in some environments
they may be symbolic constants.


Processing expectations


&format.inline; &pexp.moreinfo;




&errorcode.parents.gen;
&errorcode.children.gen;

Attributes

moreinfo



If MoreInfo is set to RefEntry,
it implies that a RefEntry exists which further describes the
ErrorCode.





